## Brand Principles

Our brand is rooted in three principles which reflect who we are, how we work, and the benefit we bring for customers.

### People
Our software's great, our people are even better. They're what make us different. We're a people business, built on the knowledge and skills of an outstanding team.

### Partnership
We're here to make a difference to our customers. That's why we build strong relationships with them, because only by working together can we both achieve so much more.

### Performance
We're only judged on getting results that benefit our customers and their business — so we always make sure they get the very best from their AMOS investment.

