## Approved Language | Plain Speaking Guide

Always use the simpler, more human alternative:

| Don't say | Say instead |
|---|---|
| Client | Customer |
| Inform | Tell |
| Commence | Start |
| Ensure | Make sure |
| Allows | Lets |
| In the event of | If |
| Receive | Get |
| Require | Need |
| Regarding | About |
| Terminate | End |
| Whilst | While |
| We will | We'll |
| Reach out | Get in touch |

